== Characteristics ==
'''Reapers''' are a class of [[Weapons (Dark Souls II)|weapon]] in ''[[Dark Souls II]]''. Reaper Class Weapons are characterized by a generally long handle leading to a curving blade, the most common example of which is the classic [[Great Scythe (Dark Souls II)|Great Scythe]].

These weapons, similarly toÂ [[Halberds (Dark Souls II)|Halberds]], must be used at a certain range to be effective, and some of them have part of the Halberd moveset themselves. However, the advantage of using Reapers lies in the fact that at the proper range, the weapon will completely bypass shields, making it a very attractive weapon in [[Player versus Player (Dark Souls II)|PvP]] combat, as many players often rely on shields.

Unfortunately they are relatively easy to [[Parry and Riposte (Dark Souls II)|parry]].

